{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"0":"The Book of the Sunnah"},"section_detail":{"0":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":266,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":266}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":22,"arabicnumber":22,"text":"Rapporté par Abu Salamah : Abu Hurairah a dit à un homme : \"Ô fils de mon frère, quand je te rapporte un hadith du Messager d’Allah (ﷺ), ne cherche pas à lui trouver des exemples","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":0,"hadith":22}}]}